node.title: One person has drowned, another missing in ManawatÅ« River
node.description: The pair went swimming in the river near the Palmerston North suburb of Awapuni.
node.content: ["A man swimming in the Manawat\u016b River in Palmerston North this evening has drowned, Water Safety New Zealand understands. A second man remains missing.", "It's believed the pair went swimming in the river near the suburb of Awapuni.", "Police said in a statement earlier this evening that emergency services received reports from the public just after 5:30pm.", "They said a further update would be provided once they had more information.", "This comes just four days after a 27-year-old woman and 11-year-old child went missing when they entered the river.", "Police have recovered the body of the girl but the woman remains missing.", "After that incident a r\u0101hui was placed on the river through the city.", "RNZ"]
